title: weird shapes on profile tab???
body:
There's these weird shapes on me and my friends profile tabs, like one will look like the Dota 2 logo and sometimes one that has a book with a flame in it, my friends have one with a piece of grass looking thing. what are these??

i dont really know how to get a picture of it on here though.....

replies.body: If I understand correctly, I think you're referring to the frequently played section of your friends list.  When you mouse over a friend in the friends list, the symbols represent what role and champion they frequently play.  For example, the grass represents the jungle role!  I hope that helps clear things up!
It does, thanks, thats so cool how it does that.
